                  Semaglutide is often a long-term treatment. We help you develop a maintenance plan that works for your lifestyle.
                </div>
              </details>
              <details class="group rounded-xl border border-neutral-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
                <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 font-medium text-neutral-900">
